    {
      "id": "prompt_1",
      "provider": "prompt",
      "name": "Triage Prompt",
      "config": {
        "instructions": [
          "You are Stage 1 of 3 (Triage) in a data-privacy compliance pipeline. You will NOT see the later Verdict or Audit stages — do only triage extraction.",
          "The input below has already been redacted of PII by an upstream step (names/emails/phones/etc. appear as block characters, e.g. █████). Do not attempt to reconstruct redacted values.",
          "The input contains two marked sections: [USER_DESCRIPTION] the redacted data-handling description, and [RETRIEVED_REGULATIONS] a short list of regulation entries a retrieval step matched to this description — this is NOT a fixed list, it is whatever was retrieved for this specific case, and it is your ONLY valid source for regulation_guess.",
          "Extract: practice (short description of the data-handling practice at issue), data_type (kind of personal data involved), jurisdiction (EU, California US, or unclear), regulation_guess (must be exactly one id from [RETRIEVED_REGULATIONS] — never invent one or use one not listed there), and risk_level (low, medium, or high).",
          "Output ONLY a single JSON object, no prose, no markdown code fences: {\"practice\": string, \"data_type\": string, \"jurisdiction\": string, \"regulation_guess\": string, \"risk_level\": string, \"redacted_text_seen\": string (echo the [USER_DESCRIPTION] text verbatim, once, so the caller can verify redaction happened)}"
        ]
      },
      "ui": { "position": { "x": 950, "y": -190 }, "nodeType": "default", "formDataValid": true },
      "input": [ { "lane": "questions", "from": "question_1" } ]
    },
    {
      "id": "guardrails_input_1",
      "provider": "guardrails",
      "name": "Guardrails — input safety",
      "config": {
        "profile": "custom",
        "custom": {
          "policy_mode": "block",
          "enable_prompt_injection": true,
          "enable_content_safety": false,
